Class Order

java.lang.Object
com.commercetools.graphql.api.types.Order
All Implemented Interfaces:
ReferenceExpandable, Versioned
public class Order extends Object implements Versioned, ReferenceExpandable
An order can be created from a cart, usually after a checkout process has been completed. [documentation](https://docs.commercetools.com/api/projects/orders)
